        >
            <div class="max-w-3xl">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold capitalize sm:text-4xl">
                    I am a woman phoenomenally. Phoenomenally women that's me.
                </h2>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
                <div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden sm:h-80 lg:h-full">
                    <img
                        alt="Persona taking a picture"
                        src="https://source.unsplash.com/DokE5D4GbDk"
                        class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
                    />
                </div>

                <div class="lg:py-16">
                    <article class="space-y-4 text-black">
                        <p
                            class="font text-xl font-semibold capitalize leading-relaxed sm:text-2xl"
                        >
                            Hi, I'm Phoebe
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing
                            elit. Aut qui hic atque tenetur quis eius quos ea
                            neque sunt, accusantium soluta minus veniam tempora
                            deserunt? Molestiae eius quidem quam repellat.
                        </p>

