                    ></path>
                </svg>
                <p
                    class="text-xl font-semibold capitalize italic leading-relaxed sm:text-2xl"
                >
                    I would like to be known as an intelligent woman, a
                    courageous woman, a loving woman, a woman who teaches by
                    being
                </p>
                <span
                    class="mb-6 mt-8 inline-block h-1 w-10 rounded bg-gray-500"
                ></span>
                <h2
                    class="title-font text-sm font-medium tracking-wider text-gray-900 lg:text-base"
                >
                    Maya Angelou
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-500">Poet</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

